Vivid colours, weightless fabrics and surreal silhouettes – @giambattistavalliparis serves up a lucid dream this season. Key Makeup Artist @helenevasnier helped us enter into the designer’s subconscious mind with strong yet simple looks starring warm brick red lips, fresh faces and dramatic “M·A·C Black Liners.” Bring your own look to life with:
🖤Matte Lipstick in Chili
🖤Pro Longwear Fluidline in Blacktrack
🖤In Extreme Dimension 3D Black Lash
🖤Amplified Lipstick in Blankety
🖤Studio Fix Sculpt And Shape Contour Palette
